01:03.411 --> 01:06.718
As I
pondered in silence,

01:06.805 --> 01:16.337
returning upon my poems,
considering, lingering long,

01:16.424 --> 01:26.042
a phantom arose before me
with distrustful aspect,

01:26.129 --> 01:30.177
in beauty, age--

01:31.961 --> 01:33.005
--and power.

01:37.662 --> 01:39.055
Looks like the
guy is a squatter.

01:39.142 --> 01:39.925
Bathroom is locked.

01:40.012 --> 01:41.666
No key.

01:41.753 --> 01:42.754
Unarmed?

01:42.841 --> 01:43.841
Seems likely.

01:55.289 --> 01:56.290
Clear.

02:21.358 --> 02:22.751
Police.

02:22.838 --> 02:24.144
Open the door.

02:24.231 --> 02:27.016
Come out slowly,
with your hands up.

02:27.103 --> 02:28.235
Open the door.

02:29.497 --> 02:31.107
Buddy, you can't stay in there.

02:31.194 --> 02:32.848
- I
- should be telling

02:32.935 --> 02:34.937
this with a sigh, somewhere
ages and ages hence.

02:35.024 --> 02:37.113
If you
don't open the door, sir,

02:37.200 --> 02:38.680
I'm going to have
to break it down.

02:41.378 --> 02:42.834
Two roads
diverged in a wood.

02:42.858 --> 02:43.965
Let
me find me something

02:43.989 --> 02:45.774
to knock this door down.

02:45.861 --> 02:49.212
And I, I took
the one less traveled by.

02:49.299 --> 02:51.083
And that has made
all the difference.

02:51.171 --> 02:52.844
You're going
to have to open the door.

02:57.046 --> 02:57.742
Go.

02:57.829 --> 02:58.829
Go, go, go.

03:05.359 --> 03:06.359
Contact right!

03:11.539 --> 03:12.907
Disturb
us, Lord, when

03:12.931 --> 03:16.108
we are too well
pleased with ourselves,

03:16.196 --> 03:20.635
when our dreams have come
true, because we have dreamed

03:20.722 --> 03:25.770
too little, when we
arrive safely because we

03:25.857 --> 03:29.209
sailed too close to the shore.

03:29.296 --> 03:32.168
Do you see that
guy loading his RPG?

03:32.255 --> 03:33.387
Got him.

03:39.436 --> 03:40.350
I'm going in!

03:40.437 --> 03:41.437
FRAG out

04:05.419 --> 04:06.507
Is he dead?

04:06.594 --> 04:08.030
West side target building.

04:08.117 --> 04:08.857
Goddamn!

04:08.944 --> 04:09.684
Morley's dead!

04:09.771 --> 04:10.772
Ghost!

04:10.859 --> 04:12.861
Get in the fucking fight.

04:12.948 --> 04:13.948
Tally

04:17.822 --> 04:18.822
Cover!

04:22.130 --> 04:23.219
Shit!

04:23.306 --> 04:24.220
God!

04:24.307 --> 04:25.177
God, it was too fucking

04:25.265 --> 04:25.917
close.

04:26.004 --> 04:26.657
You good?

04:26.744 --> 04:27.397
I'm good.

04:27.484 --> 04:28.137
I'm good.

04:28.224 --> 04:29.051
I owe you.

04:29.138 --> 04:29.834
You owe me shit.

04:29.921 --> 04:31.053
Hey, Sammy.

04:31.140 --> 04:32.140
Listen.

04:33.969 --> 04:34.969
Listen, listen.

04:37.451 --> 04:38.887
Are we clear?

04:38.974 --> 04:39.974
Clear.

04:53.467 --> 04:54.076
Let's move.

04:54.163 --> 04:54.685
Hey!

04:54.772 --> 04:55.599
Hey!

04:55.686 --> 04:56.252
You fucking crazy?

04:56.339 --> 04:57.384
What?

04:57.471 --> 04:58.167
They got him turned around, man.

04:58.254 --> 04:59.081
No, Ghost.

04:59.168 --> 04:59.864
We wait here, man.

04:59.951 --> 05:00.604
They baitin' us.

05:00.691 --> 05:02.171
What are you doing?

05:02.258 --> 05:03.409
I'm going to loan you a
pair of men's underwear.

05:03.433 --> 05:04.129
You stain them, you own them.

05:04.216 --> 05:04.782
You keep them.

05:04.869 --> 05:05.348
Yeah.

05:05.435 --> 05:06.001
Let me know.

05:06.088 --> 05:07.481
Braden

05:12.007 --> 05:12.877
I got it.

05:12.964 --> 05:13.661
I've got it, Ghost.

05:13.748 --> 05:14.748
I've got it.

05:15.445 --> 05:16.098
There you go.

05:16.185 --> 05:16.925
Bring it.

05:17.012 --> 05:18.012
There you go.

05:20.145 --> 05:22.974
This is the the last
motherfucker I'd thought I'd be

05:23.061 --> 05:26.413
slung over my shoulder.

05:26.500 --> 05:28.110
I said I'm not
feeling it, Ghost.

05:28.197 --> 05:30.112
Well, you can tell
everybody you led the way.

05:30.199 --> 05:31.243
I'm the First Sergeant.

05:31.331 --> 05:32.438
I say we stay the fuck here.

05:32.462 --> 05:33.158
Atta boy.

05:33.245 --> 05:34.116
Stack up!

05:34.203 --> 05:35.203
Why?

05:37.467 --> 05:40.078
You're an ass.

05:40.165 --> 05:41.165
On three!

05:44.344 --> 05:45.344
Three!

05:47.085 --> 05:48.085
God!

05:51.873 --> 05:53.570
Fuck!

05:53.657 --> 05:55.180
Motherfuckers!

05:59.228 --> 05:59.924
Hey!

06:00.011 --> 06:01.011
Let me go!

06:03.232 --> 06:04.232
Put the cuffs.

06:09.020 --> 06:10.020
Get him up.

06:11.849 --> 06:12.849
Walk!

06:14.461 --> 06:15.375
No!

06:15.462 --> 06:16.376
No!

06:16.463 --> 06:17.986
Don't do this!

06:18.073 --> 06:19.379
Don't do this!

06:19.466 --> 06:20.989
I need a medic!

06:21.076 --> 06:24.384
I need a medic!

06:24.471 --> 06:25.907
Believe this guy?

06:25.994 --> 06:27.082
Something else.

06:30.477 --> 06:34.176
All right, buddy.

06:34.263 --> 06:35.873
Let's see.

06:35.960 --> 06:37.745
You've got anything
shoved in your pockets?

06:37.832 --> 06:39.050
Anything going to prick me?

06:40.356 --> 06:41.749
As
to me, directing

06:41.836 --> 06:46.841
like flame, its eyes
with finger pointing

06:46.928 --> 06:49.147
to many immortal songs.

06:49.234 --> 06:51.149
Take a break.

06:51.236 --> 06:58.200
A menacing voice,
what singest thou, it said.

06:58.287 --> 07:03.118
Knowest thou not there is but
one theme forever enduring

07:03.205 --> 07:04.946
bards.

07:05.033 --> 07:08.689
And that is the theme of war.

07:08.776 --> 07:10.995
The fortune of battles.

07:11.082 --> 07:15.609
The making of perfect soldiers.

07:25.445 --> 07:27.708
Hey, Tony!

07:27.795 --> 07:29.274
What you doing?

07:29.361 --> 07:30.450
Let me get that for you.

07:30.537 --> 07:31.537
He's got it.

07:35.803 --> 07:37.587
Looks like they knew you

07:37.674 --> 07:38.674
That's funny.

07:41.156 --> 07:42.636
Who tagged it?

07:42.723 --> 07:44.551
I don't know.

07:44.638 --> 07:48.642
Locals, gang bangers, who knows?

07:48.729 --> 07:50.252
Who's the kid?

07:50.339 --> 07:51.339
He's Pete.

07:54.735 --> 07:56.432
You got any paying work?

07:56.519 --> 07:57.825
No.

07:57.912 --> 08:00.218
And none coming down
the line either.

08:00.305 --> 08:03.178
Sorry about that, bud.

08:03.265 --> 08:06.137
You said Venice
Boulevard moved out.

08:06.224 --> 08:08.575
Extended their lease.

08:08.662 --> 08:11.578
How about that
building you just bought?

08:11.665 --> 08:12.665
It's in escrow.

08:16.060 --> 08:17.279
All right.

08:17.366 --> 08:20.587
Did you get a new bike?

08:20.674 --> 08:22.502
Yeah.

08:22.589 --> 08:25.287
You mind if we settle up on
the last little bit of work?

08:25.374 --> 08:29.465
Pete, take five.

08:29.552 --> 08:31.946
You want to settle up?

08:32.033 --> 08:33.513
Of course.

08:33.600 --> 08:36.472
Come here.

08:36.558 --> 08:48.963
There you go.

08:49.050 --> 08:51.792
Actually it comes
to a whole lot more.

08:51.879 --> 08:52.619
That's it.

08:52.706 --> 08:54.534
We're settled.

08:54.621 --> 08:56.623
I'm not clear.

08:56.710 --> 08:58.581
You're not clear.

08:58.668 --> 09:00.104
OK.

09:00.191 --> 09:03.151
Well, you want me to
explain it to you?

09:03.238 --> 09:04.892
You spent the two
weeks that you were

09:04.979 --> 09:07.459
meant to be working doing
pull ups off the side

09:07.547 --> 09:09.113
of that building in the alley.

09:09.200 --> 09:11.463
And I caught you
reading more than once.

09:11.551 --> 09:12.813
During my breaks.

09:12.900 --> 09:13.770
What breaks?

09:13.857 --> 09:14.684
What are you, union?

09:14.771 --> 09:16.251
There's no breaks.

09:16.338 --> 09:17.881
You're working four
to five hours a day.

09:17.905 --> 09:18.645
If it falls on your
lunch, that's fine.

09:18.732 --> 09:20.429
But there's no breaks.

09:20.516 --> 09:22.997
The VA docs says to exercise
to keep my heart rate up

09:23.084 --> 09:24.476
so I get oxygen to my brain.

09:24.564 --> 09:25.608
Yeah.

09:25.695 --> 09:27.567
I don't want to get into it.

09:27.654 --> 09:29.588
And they told me to read to
take my mind off other things.

09:29.612 --> 09:34.791
So can-- can you just pay me
the rest of what you owe me?

09:34.878 --> 09:41.015
Look, I'm going to make
this plain and simple for you.

09:41.102 --> 09:44.584
I am not paying you to get fit.

09:44.671 --> 09:46.368
OK?

09:46.455 --> 09:48.588
You want to fuck around,
there's plenty other assholes

09:48.675 --> 09:50.546
you can work for.

09:50.633 --> 09:53.027
Not like you.

09:53.114 --> 09:58.772
You're just like all
of them, looking for a handout.

09:58.859 --> 10:01.557
My injury's real, bro.

10:01.644 --> 10:04.038
Your injury's real?

10:04.125 --> 10:07.563
Then you should do
what your doctor said.

10:07.650 --> 10:10.740
He told you to read, bro?

10:10.827 --> 10:14.831
Then get a job as a librarian.

10:14.918 --> 10:15.789
You know what?

10:15.876 --> 10:17.747
You built the house.

10:17.834 --> 10:18.705
Own it.

10:18.792 --> 10:20.315
Pay me what you owe me.

10:21.185 --> 10:21.751
Now.

10:21.838 --> 10:22.838
Now?

10:39.029 --> 10:41.510
You enjoy living in a
country where you can mouth off

10:41.597 --> 10:44.426
to whoever, whenever?

10:44.513 --> 10:46.689
You're welcome.

10:46.776 --> 10:47.995
Thank you for that.

10:48.082 --> 10:49.300
Thank you for your service.

10:52.216 --> 10:54.436
Now get off my fucking premises.

10:54.523 --> 10:55.785
Walk away, Will.

11:01.835 --> 11:03.706
Pete, get back to it.

11:07.014 --> 11:09.451
You were the bigger man.

11:09.538 --> 11:10.539
Yeah, I mean it.

11:10.626 --> 11:11.540
You did the right thing.

11:11.627 --> 11:12.759
You walked away.

11:12.846 --> 11:15.631
I wanted to beat his ass.

11:15.718 --> 11:18.590
Understandable.

11:18.678 --> 11:19.940
Well, it's good
to know I still

11:20.027 --> 11:21.419
got a little fight left in me.

11:21.506 --> 11:22.769
I was ready to go, man.

11:22.856 --> 11:23.856
I bet.

11:25.902 --> 11:28.470
And he was a big
son-of-a-bitch.

11:28.557 --> 11:29.732
How big?

11:29.819 --> 11:31.386
6'4 or 6'5.

11:31.473 --> 11:32.169
6'5?

11:32.256 --> 11:32.822
Yeah?

11:32.909 --> 11:33.909
Ish.

11:36.043 --> 11:37.479
You know I ain't a lover.

11:37.566 --> 11:38.436
Yeah, I know.

11:38.523 --> 11:39.307
Hell no.

11:39.394 --> 11:40.308
Hell no.

11:40.395 --> 11:41.831
He was a bad ass.

11:41.918 --> 11:43.833
You know, Ghost, you
could cage fight.

11:43.920 --> 11:46.314
Well, you know I'm
younger than I look.

11:46.401 --> 11:47.097
Hey, come on, man.

11:47.184 --> 11:48.403
You look great.

11:48.490 --> 11:49.230
You mean that?

11:49.317 --> 11:50.535
I mean that.

11:50.622 --> 11:51.623
Fuck, yeah, I mean it.

11:51.711 --> 11:55.062
You could model, probably.

11:55.149 --> 11:57.368
Look at this face.

11:57.455 --> 11:59.719
You could model.

11:59.806 --> 12:01.155
Great way to meet girls.

12:05.246 --> 12:08.684
I bet this guy
meets a lot of girls.

12:08.771 --> 12:10.817
Hell, yeah, he does.

12:10.904 --> 12:12.166
All right.

12:12.253 --> 12:15.952
Now they say that
you ain't drunk

12:16.039 --> 12:20.652
if you can lay on the
ground without holding on.

12:20.740 --> 12:21.740
And who's "they"?

12:21.784 --> 12:23.786
The experts.

12:23.873 --> 12:24.787
OK.

12:24.874 --> 12:27.616
Let's see.

12:27.703 --> 12:28.443
Shit.

12:28.530 --> 12:29.530
I'm sober.

12:30.880 --> 12:32.403
All right.

12:32.490 --> 12:33.903
Hands down on the board
beside your shoulders.

12:33.927 --> 12:35.450
OK.

12:35.537 --> 12:36.819
Palms down, like you're
going to do a push-up.

12:36.843 --> 12:38.453
All right.

12:38.540 --> 12:40.847
And you thrust your
upper body up in the sky--

12:40.934 --> 12:42.587
You look like you're
fucking a crab hole.

12:42.674 --> 12:47.592
--and you sweep your
legs underneath you, and--

12:47.679 --> 12:50.465
I hope you can swim.

12:50.552 --> 12:52.032
Why?

12:52.119 --> 12:54.469
Because you ain't even
on the board, Ghost.

12:54.556 --> 12:55.556
Shit.

12:58.255 --> 12:59.255
Yeah.

13:02.259 --> 13:03.086
Hey.

13:03.173 --> 13:03.739
Give me a second.

13:03.826 --> 13:04.479
Hey.

13:04.566 --> 13:05.567
Hey, hey.

13:05.654 --> 13:07.917
Ghost, don't go over here.

13:08.004 --> 13:09.266
Now those are friends of mine.

13:09.353 --> 13:10.920
I see them down
here all the time.

13:11.007 --> 13:12.007
Ghost.

13:14.141 --> 13:15.446
What are you talking about?

13:15.533 --> 13:17.884
Why would you say that?

13:17.971 --> 13:20.234
Listen to me.

13:20.321 --> 13:21.539
You're not looking for him.

13:24.586 --> 13:27.589
So you leave him alone.

13:27.676 --> 13:28.676
I mean it.

13:31.680 --> 13:32.680
Ghost?

13:50.612 --> 13:52.092
You'll be all right.

13:56.009 --> 13:57.488
Wait!

13:57.575 --> 14:00.361
You-- you forgot--
you forgot your kiss!

14:00.448 --> 14:02.493
His lips must
be getting tired.

14:02.580 --> 14:04.626
I ain't going to
watch a soldier beg.

14:04.713 --> 14:05.409
Pisses me off.

14:05.496 --> 14:06.410
Let's pass him.

14:06.497 --> 14:09.631
Moving, on the right.

14:09.718 --> 14:11.111
Spare some change.

14:11.198 --> 14:12.895
A comedian.

14:12.982 --> 14:14.027
Aw, man!

14:14.114 --> 14:15.942
I'm just screwing with you.

14:16.029 --> 14:17.813
Yo, smile!

14:17.900 --> 14:20.163
It's a celebration.

14:20.250 --> 14:22.470
What we celebrating?

14:22.557 --> 14:24.602
That we're rich.

14:24.689 --> 14:29.303
Did not God choose the poor of
this world to be rich in faith,

14:29.390 --> 14:30.957
and heirs to the
kingdom which he

14:31.044 --> 14:33.829
promised to those who love him?

14:33.916 --> 14:34.830
The who and the what?

14:34.917 --> 14:36.005
The what?

14:36.092 --> 14:38.399
Are you military?

14:38.486 --> 14:39.356
'Nam.

14:39.443 --> 14:40.792
'71.

14:40.880 --> 14:42.490
Is that boonie
part of your uniform?

14:42.577 --> 14:43.621
Was.

14:43.708 --> 14:46.146
So what's all that crap on it?

14:46.233 --> 14:48.104
Shit I've collected.

14:48.191 --> 14:51.542
Well, can you clean it up
and show a little respect?

14:51.629 --> 14:53.805
You do that?

14:53.893 --> 14:55.807
What, you don't agree?

14:55.895 --> 14:57.374
This going to take long?

14:57.461 --> 14:58.656
I got a 2 o'clock
tee-time and 18 hole--

14:58.680 --> 14:59.986
Go ahead.

15:00.073 --> 15:01.393
Hey, is this thing
in park, Ghost?

15:06.166 --> 15:07.254
Bless you, brother.

15:12.520 --> 15:17.917
It enrages me and
it breaks my heart

15:18.004 --> 15:21.616
to see people that serve this
country standing on the streets

15:21.703 --> 15:22.703
begging for scraps.

15:22.747 --> 15:23.747
You with me?

15:30.712 --> 15:37.023
I know that you know
how to wear this.

15:37.110 --> 15:39.112
But just in case you forgot.

15:42.289 --> 15:44.117
You wear any piece
of this uniform,

15:44.204 --> 15:46.902
you stand tall proud, hooah?

15:46.989 --> 15:49.035
Hooah.

15:49.122 --> 15:51.472
You fought for this country.

15:51.559 --> 15:53.691
I did indeed.

15:53.778 --> 15:54.778
Remember that.

15:58.435 --> 15:59.784
You take care of yourself.

16:02.831 --> 16:03.919
Moving.

16:04.006 --> 16:05.006
Moving.

16:14.321 --> 16:17.802
Thanks, babe.

16:17.889 --> 16:19.979
How is it?

16:20.066 --> 16:22.111
Rocky fucking road.

16:22.198 --> 16:24.853
It's like Run DMC, shit
never gets old, man.

16:30.119 --> 16:32.141
Peter Piper picked
peppers, but Run rapped rhymes.

16:32.165 --> 16:33.688
Hey, read me this.

16:33.775 --> 16:34.689
No.

16:34.776 --> 16:36.560
For me.

16:36.647 --> 16:37.755
Come on, Ghost, can I just
sit and eat my ice cream?

16:37.779 --> 16:39.172
Come on.

16:39.259 --> 16:40.323
It'll take my mind
off the calories.

16:40.347 --> 16:42.088
I ain't your book bitch, man.

16:42.175 --> 16:45.308
No, but you could be.

16:45.395 --> 16:48.703
Why don't you just get a
book on tape or some shit?

16:48.790 --> 16:49.790
Dude.

16:51.749 --> 17:01.803
Today, across
our fathers graves,

17:01.890 --> 17:08.375
the astonished years reveal the
remnant of that desperate host

17:08.462 --> 17:12.814
which cleansed our
East with steel.

17:20.343 --> 17:21.493
Troop's had contact.

17:21.518 --> 17:22.824
Reinforce to Bravo checkpoint.

17:25.218 --> 17:26.696
I'm gonna pull off.

17:40.755 --> 17:42.061
God damn!

17:44.106 --> 17:45.151
Wait!

17:45.238 --> 17:48.632
Clarence Miller's been shot!

17:49.720 --> 17:50.634
Cover!

17:50.721 --> 17:51.721
They're moving left.

17:53.550 --> 17:54.986
Get him up against the tire.

17:55.074 --> 17:56.292
He's shot in the neck.

17:56.379 --> 17:57.424
My neck!

17:57.511 --> 18:00.557
Put pressure on that wound.

18:00.644 --> 18:02.298
Hail and farewell!

18:02.385 --> 18:04.996
We greet you here, with
tears that none will scorn--

18:05.084 --> 18:09.175
O keepers of the House of
old, or ever we were born!

18:09.262 --> 18:10.698
I want my money.

18:10.785 --> 18:12.110
What do you mean
you want your money?

18:12.134 --> 18:12.961
I told you to get
off my property!

18:13.048 --> 18:13.962
You owe me $145!

18:14.049 --> 18:14.615
Get off my property!

18:14.702 --> 18:15.529
I worked for you!

18:15.616 --> 18:16.878
You owe me money.

18:16.965 --> 18:17.879
I told you to get
off my premises.

18:17.966 --> 18:18.966
Now get out of here.

18:19.707 --> 18:21.317
That's assault!

18:21.404 --> 18:23.252
If you can
force your heart and nerve

18:23.276 --> 18:25.582
and sinew to serve your turn
long after they are gone,

18:25.669 --> 18:29.369
and so hold on when there is
nothing in you except the Will

18:29.456 --> 18:32.328
which says to them: "Hold on!"

18:32.415 --> 18:33.938
I am going to call the police.

